ATTRIBUTION NOTICE:

This project incorporates and builds upon the context engineering methodology
and templates created by Cole Medin (https://github.com/coleam00) from his
"context-engineering-intro" repository (https://github.com/coleam00/context-engineering-intro).

The original methodology, templates, and examples are used with attribution
under open source principles. All credit for the context engineering approach
and foundational templates belongs to Cole Medin.

Cole Medin's original work is the foundation that makes this MCP server
implementation possible. Please visit his repository to learn more about
the methodology and to contribute to the original templates.